<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="-real-world-applications">üìà Real-World Applications<a href="https://mongodb-developer.github.io/mongodb-rag/blog/2025/03/15/workshop-introduction#-real-world-applications" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to üìà Real-World Applications" title="Direct link to üìà Real-World Applications">‚Äã</a></h2>
